{"tid":1422319,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「機場展覽」所有人入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-06T10:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:11:48.000Z","uid":17502,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"52449e94b17d74971740a0a85ceebaa4e73fb001","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"隔離po話想係機場搞個展覽，我搞過展覽，我有啲建議。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">idea</span></span><br />\n<br />\n- 展覽要分區，最少要分為事件陳述，抗爭模式，影片區，留言區，等等等等。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事件陳述</span><br />\n- 展覽要有大標題，要有成個展覽嘅introduction，大大塊板俾人知你個展覽係講緊乜，最緊要係有清楚表達我哋嘅5大訴求<br />\n<br />\n- 可以從第一日發射催淚彈開始，將所有收集返嚟嘅彈頭排成tineline，講返曬成件事出嚟，要係最當眼嘅地方擺，要多語言，要言簡意賅，要有震撼性嘅圖，宜精簡不宜多<br />\n<br />\n- 如果有傷者願意出嚟，可以作為活生生嘅展品，坐返係你受傷嘅時段<br />\n<br />\n- 如果有其他相關物件，都可以當係展品展出<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗爭手法</span><br />\n- 另外一個區可以擺抗爭手法，抗爭者頭盔，裝備，衣物等，全部都要有備註寫明咩嚟，點用，點解用<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">影片區</span><br />\n- 影片區主要可以搵人剪條高官bull shit片，要有佢哋荒謬嘅言論<br />\n<br />\n- 另外可以剪條警察濫權片，展現佢哋嘅黑暗<br />\n<br />\n- 警黑合作片，唔好放過老豆老母墳頭自己跌低個垃圾<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">留言區</span><br />\n- 留言區係俾觀眾留言，寫低支持字句用，如有人反對，都絕對唔可以撕走，唔可以展開罵戰，我哋會尊重，雖然唔認同<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">design &amp; setup</span><br />\n- 顏色係黑色為主<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可能短期內係機場做好一套wayfinding system，所以需要人手係各個出入口，接機口，check in counter舉牌，引導人去個展覽<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n要成事，大家要搵到展品，搵到人寫中立嘅contents，搵到editor，搵到designer，搵到傷者，搵到其他在場人手及幫手set up嘅人手。<br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁"},{"pid":"e3a58b52643fee335e20510f84db562dbdd8f233","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:28:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e26301141fd073ae225b2b9222d4d7b856b41364","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:29:33.000Z","msg":"十連無人理收皮"},{"pid":"2cc5205184699bb386b254fbdf7a70a5d1178fd6","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:29:45.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f5259ade7fa8ecb15688d89aa85549a093bc22cf","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:29:55.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"7939031e1ae81c6fc2912cbfd5e56ea6e1117185","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:30:07.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"88fcfcaed6b1c980aa2a3802972bc0252e228db2","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:30:17.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"bb1cbd61a4cdcd5e232a7167f6084f1f9d69f7ee","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"5c8ef8e1119877659b5b2f6402cfaa6bb89addb9","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:30:37.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"e7f2b3c216f5cac05c7b868aaa1eb06c7edb742c","tid":1422319,"uid":281720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1045ade2ffb8cca65d7366aae039518fa66f95d","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"1ac20c88adb3e1c946937c6651e6488bc1018239","tid":1422319,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:31:01.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"66f5de16cb0c4816f356aa2